itunes:title: Aisha Praught Leer - Commonwealth Games Gold Medalist
title: Aisha Praught Leer - Commonwealth Games Gold Medalist
description:
Absolute pleasure, talking to fellow UA pro athlete, Aisha,

We talk:

* What it takes to win Com Games Gold
* Training group, relationship with group members and how that can help success
* How invested Aisha is, and what it takes to be an athlete at her level
* Aisha is completely Dairy free, and how that's helped her training / Performances

Can I just repeat - Commonwealth Games GOLD medalist.

Pleasure.

Support the show
